   <tbody> 
    <tr> 
     <th style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"> <h2>Loretta's Greatbow</h2> </th> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"><img title="Loretta's Greatbow" src="/file/Elden-Ring/lorettas_greatbow_sorcery_elden_ring_wiki_guide_200px.png" alt="lorettas greatbow sorcery elden ring wiki guide 200px" width="200" height="200"></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>Spell Type</td> 
     <td><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Loretta's Sorceries" href="/Loretta's+Sorceries" target="">Loretta's Sorceries</a></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>FP Cost 24</td> 
     <td>Slots Used 1</td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td colspan="2"><img title="item_effect_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_18px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/item_effects_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_55px_18px.png" alt="item effects icon elden ring wiki guide 55px 18px" width="18" height="18">Effect 
      <div class="lineleft">
        Fires great arrow from a magic greatbow 
      </div> <br><img style="float: left;" title="Attributes Requirement" src="/file/Elden-Ring/attributes-required-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18.png" alt="attributes required elden ring wiki guide 18" width="18" height="18">Requires 
      <div class="lineleft"> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Intelligence" href="/Intelligence" target="">Intelligence</a> 26 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Faith" href="/Faith" target="">Faith</a>&nbsp;0 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Arcane" href="/Arcane" target="">Arcane</a>&nbsp;0 
      </div> </td> 
    </tr> 
   </tbody> 
  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Loretta's Greatbow</strong> is a&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Sorceries" href="/Sorceries" target="">Sorcery</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. <strong>Loretta's Greatbow spell</strong> creates a bow that fires a projectile. Can be charged to further increase damage. Updated to&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>Sorcery used by Royal Knight Loretta.<br><br>Creates a magic greatbow and fires a great arrow.<br>Charging enhances potency. Hold to keep the great arrow nocked.<br><br>It is said that the bow was Loretta's favored weapon.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Loretta's Greatbow</h3> 
<p>Where to find <strong>Loretta's Greatbow</strong>:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li> <p><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Caria Manor" href="/Caria+Manor" target="">Caria Manor</a>: Dropped by <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Royal Knight Loretta" href="/Royal+Knight+Loretta" target="">Royal Knight Loretta</a> upon defeat. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring interactive map?id=8823&amp;code=mapA" href="/interactive+map?id=8823&amp;code=mapA">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Video Location" href="https://youtu.be/neQ-5QWwtI0?t=2006">Video Location</a></p> </li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Loretta's Greatbow Guide</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Loretta's Sorceries" href="/Loretta's+Sorceries">Loretta's Sorcery</a></li> 
 <li>Stamina Cost:&nbsp;30</li> 
 <li>Deals magic damage</li> 
 <li>Hold R1 to charge this Spell up. Once full charged it will flash for a second for increased damage.</li> 
 <li>&nbsp;<span style="color: #ff6600;"><em>NOTE:</em></span>&nbsp;Since&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>&nbsp;FP Consumption has been Decreased from 28 to 24.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3>&nbsp;Elden Ring Loretta's Greatbow Notes &amp; Tips</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>This spell is immune to the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Ash of War: Thops's Barrier" href="/Ash+of+War:+Thops's+Barrier">Thops's Barrier Ash of War</a>, and will penetrate the spell parry attempt.</li> 
 <li>This spell cannot be boosted by <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Arrow's Sting Talisman" href="/Arrow's+Sting+Talisman">Arrow's Sting Talisman</a></li> 
 <li>When fully charged, this spell is affected by <a class="wiki_link wiki_tooltip" title="Elden Ring Godfrey Icon" href="/Godfrey+Icon">Godfrey Icon</a>.</li> 
 <li>The spell does no bonus damage from charging unless unless fully charged.</li> 
 <li>If fully charged, it does roughly 22% more damage.</li> 
 <li>Spell has exceptionally high range, making it an excellent opening move against bosses, or as a tool for hitting hard to deal with enemies from a distance.</li> 
 <li>Updated to patch&nbsp;<strong>1.07</strong>. See&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes" target="">Patch Notes</a>&nbsp;for details.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Best Loretta's Greatbow Buffs</h3> 
<p>Use these&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Buffs and Debuffs" href="/Buffs+and+Debuffs">Buffs</a>&nbsp;to maximize the performance of Loretta's Greatbow spell. Note that increases in attack power are multiplicative unless stated otherwise.</p> 
