				<li id="16501813" class="cmnt-root" data="21" data-d="1647173545000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578560/Loretta's-Greatbow" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">13 Mar 2022 08:12</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16501813" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">this spell surprisingly provides a cheesy win for any open-space field bosses: riding a horse, finding a safe spot where the boss slowly approaching you since you don&apos;t have the aggro, shoot the charged bow, run as far away as you can to deaggro, repeat and rinse until the boss health bar is depleted, its a slow process and requires lots of fp (10+ flasks recommended for any mid-late field bosses) tho.<br/><br/>At late game when fp is no longer an issue, its actually a surprisingly good spell because of its insane range: you can get access of sniper area that is really safe for the annoying dangerous minions compared with pebble or rock slings. After using this spell, I feel like this game (dungeon exploration part) has become a position plotting/puzzle solving game where the puzzle is to find the best position to slay the enemies.<br/><br/>Some bad thing about this bow is its large projectile: if the shooting angle is too large, it can easily hit the ground you are standing even though visually speaking the spell shall hit the target surely. In that situation please use pebble if possible.</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16501813" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16501813" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">1</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>24</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>3</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16501813"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16501813" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16501813"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
