				<li id="16449694" class="cmnt-root" data="1" data-d="1646391287000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578560/Loretta's-Greatbow" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">04 Mar 2022 05:54</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16449694" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">Unfortunately, an extremely niche spell. The damage/FP cost is horrendous. It&apos;s one saving grace is that MASSIVE range, giving it one niche as an opener/sniper. The slow casting time for both charged and uncharged versions make it unusable in most boss fights. Even horseback archery is not ideal as you cannot move at speed while charging. If you can use this to snipe at enemies or bosses in locations where the cannot hit you, then you&apos;ve got a use for it. In order for this to be more generally useful, it needs more versatility. The ideal would be for something that can fire quickly when uncharged with the option for charging, preferably with variable FP cost as well. As it stands it cannot replace a useful fast casting ranged spell like the humble but powerful Glinstone Pebble or the slower but just as potent Glintstone Blade.</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16449694" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16449694" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">3</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>11</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>10</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16449694"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16449694" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16449694"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
